                    <p class="text-muted small">Responsive front-end framework for styling, layout, and UI components.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-3">
                <div class="tech-card p-4 border rounded text-center shadow-sm">
